# AGENTS.md

## Project Goal
Build PromptForge, a SaaS prompt builder for creating, saving, sharing, and reusing structured AI prompts across multiple AI engines.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js
- React
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Prisma
- PostgreSQL
- NextAuth

## Development Rules
- Keep the UI clean, modern, and simple.
- Prioritize working MVP features before advanced features.
- Use reusable components.
- Use TypeScript types everywhere.
- Keep database schema clear and scalable.
- Add comments only where helpful.
- Do not add unnecessary dependencies.
- Run linting and type checks before completing a task.

## Initial MVP Pages
- Dashboard
- Prompt Builder
- Template Library
- Style Profiles
- Settings
- AI Comparison placeholder

## Prompt Builder Requirements
Users should be able to define:
- Role/persona
- Task objective
- Context
- Tone/personality
- Detail level
- Output format
- Constraints
- Examples
- Variables

## Template Requirements
Users should be able to:
- Save templates
- Edit templates
- Duplicate templates
- Delete templates
- Favorite templates
- Organize with folders and tags

## Output Style
Use a modern SaaS interface with card layouts, sidebar navigation, light/dark mode support, and responsive design.
